{"id":37981,"title":"Coat's-like exudation in rhodopsin retinitis pigmentosa: successful treatment with an intravitreal dexamethasone implant.","abstract":"Role of intravitreal injection of dexamethasone implant (Ozurdex) for refractory macular thickening.A case report of a 13-year-old boy with Rhodopsin-positive, CRB1-negative retinitis pigmentosa presenting with Coat's-like exudative vitreoretinopathy and treatment-resistant cystoid macular oedema.A reduction in the macular thickening following a single injection of Ozurdex.We present our experience in successful treatment of refractory macular oedema with intravitreal injection of dexamethasone implant resulting in clinically significant resolution of macular thickening.","date":"2014-04-10","categories":"Congenital Hereditary and Neonatal Diseases and Abnormalities","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24458202","annotations":[{"name":"Dexamethasone","weight":0.611663,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dexamethasone"},{"name":"Edema","weight":0.405132,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edema"},{"name":"Injection (medicine)","weight":0.358524,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Injection_(medicine)"},{"name":"Retinitis pigmentosa","weight":0.286798,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retinitis_pigmentosa"},{"name":"Redox","weight":0.176618,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Redox"},{"name":"Cutaneous conditions","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cutaneous_conditions"},{"name":"Macular edema","weight":0.0364124,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macular_edema"},{"name":"Rhodopsin","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhodopsin"},{"name":"CRB1","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRB1"},{"name":"Cystoids","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cystoids"},{"name":"Exudate","weight"